---
title: Scenario 5 — Order Change Arrives While Transfer Animating
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Service as Backend Service
    participant ParentVM as ParentViewModel
    participant Cache as SourceCache
    participant Box as AnimatedListBox
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline
    participant Anim as Transfer Animation

    User->>ParentVM: Click transfer button
    ParentVM->>ParentVM: StampTransfer(id, ToSibling, FromSibling)
    ParentVM->>Cache: cache.Edit(IsOnRight = true)
    Cache-->>Box: CollectionChanged → Transfer
    Box->>Pipeline: Transfer jumps queue\n_pipelineBusy = true
    Pipeline->>Anim: RunSlide out + RunSlide in\n_inflightCount = 2

    Note over Anim: ~60ms into 200ms transfer animation

    Service->>Cache: Order change on another item
    Note over Service: Throttle window starts

    Note over Service: More order changes may arrive\nand collapse here during the 150ms window

    Cache-->>Box: CollectionChanged (Move) after 150ms

    Box->>Box: ClassifyChange\nHasAnyPendingReason() = false\n→ ChangeType.OrderChange

    Box->>Box: _pipelineBusy = true\ncannot process now

    Box->>Pipeline: Check queue for existing OrderChange\nNone found — enqueue new one

    Note over Pipeline: Queue: [OrderChange]
    Note over Pipeline: Pipeline is busy (transfer animating)\nOrder change waits

    Note over Anim: Transfer animation completes (200ms)\n_inflightCount = 0

    Box->>Pipeline: OnAllAnimationsComplete\n_pipelineBusy = false
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: TryProcessNext\nDequeue OrderChange\n_pipelineBusy = true

    Pipeline->>Box: ProcessSnapshot(OrderChange)
    Box->>Box: OnBeforeAnimatedDiff\nCapturePreLayoutBounds\n(correctly reflects post-transfer state)
    Box->>Box: DiffVisible(reordered items)
    Box->>Box: FLIP animations play

    Box->>Box: FLIP complete\n_inflightCount = 0
    Box->>Pipeline: OnAllAnimationsComplete\n_pipelineBusy = false
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Queue empty — done

    Note over Box: Result: Transfer played fully,\nthen order change played.\nNo visual glitches.
